address.streetAddress: Aruba Bay with Basement Plan, Grande Reserve Ranch Homes

location.fullValue: Aruba Bay with Basement Plan, Grande Reserve Ranch Homes

data.description: 5 car garage, spacious ranch, water front and garden shed for all of your needs. Eat in Kitchen with hard surface counter tops and center island and living room with brick/stone fireplace and dining rm, both with large picture windows and beautiful view of Blackberry Creek and forest preserve on other side to stop future growth nearby for privacy. 2 car attached garage and detached 3 1/2 car garage (34 x 24) with electric. Office/sitting room, 3 season room on back of home with access to large 2 car garage. Back covered porch to fenced yard. Basement walls fully encapsulated for moisture and drainage tiled installed under inside of basement to sump. New well tank and pump 2022, new front sidewalk and roof 2021.
